Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed by {\c&H0000FF&\1a&H05&}JackieD2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, mankind received a grim reminder...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We lived in fear of the Titans
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and were disgraced to live in these cages we called walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Squadron, prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one target!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We will exterminate it and make this mankind's first outside base!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Target approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Split into fives!\NRemember your training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll distract the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All attack teams, prepare to move up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll close in on it from the sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a taste of mankind's strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Mikasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We should head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you in a deep sleep and think you're still dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think I was having a really long dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I dreaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\pos(992,308)}Attack on Titan Movie \N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N {\fs45}Gekijō-ban
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\pos(972,1046)}{\fs40}[ Zenpen ]  ー Guren no Yumiya ー\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N {\fs50}[ Part 1 ]  ー Crimson Bow and Arrow ー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The walls were created with God's wisdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The walls are the work of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one soul shall dare desecrate the walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone that I was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't know why you were crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should talk to your dad about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell my dad about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you crying about, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hannes-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mikasa mad at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why would I be crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You reek of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothin' wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're drinking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum... Aren't you on duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're watching the gates today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been here all day. Started getting hungry and thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:23.89,Default,,400,400,0,,But it's not a big deal if we happen to drink something with a little alcohol in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're drunk, how are you gonna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? When would we have to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really have to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When they break the wall and come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, don't say things like that out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Dr. Jaeger's son. You've got spirit, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If they do end up breaking the wall, we'll do our jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not once in the past 100 years have they broken the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:05:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Still! My dad said that it's times like these when we're in the most danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:07.82,Default,,400,400,0,,While helping in the maintenance of the wall, I see them out there, wandering aimlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:12.89,Default,,400,400,0,,But, speaking as a soldier, I don't think they can do anything about this 50 meter wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So... you don't even have the will to fight them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:25.74,Default,,300,300,0,,What?! Why don't you stop calling yourselves the Town Guards and call yourselves the Wall Menders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Has a nice ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:29.88,Default,,400,400,0,,But Eren,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When people see soldiers fighting, they know something bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:41.06,Default,,300,300,0,,Everyone's much happier when we're doing nothing and getting called useless freeloaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. We might not get out, but we'll live as long as we can eat and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're living like... like livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This kid sure knows how to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like you can do anything, right Hannes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he... want to join the Survey Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should join the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they're stupid too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying they're stupid or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Survey Corps are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The front gate is opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The heroes have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there so few of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of them were eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you get for going outside the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Moses! Moses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, Moses... I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her, Moses's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only part of him we could salvage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But... my son... was useful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He might... not have been a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but he at least died helping mankind fight back, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No... During this mission, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after all of our missions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we still haven't made any progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just gotten soldiers killed left and right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And we haven't learned anything useful about the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously. So all we've been doing is offering ourselves to them as free lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa! Fine, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the wood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you changed your mind about joining the Survey Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me pick this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Eren. I'm surprised you gathered this much firewood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ear was red. You were lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa helped you, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Dad, are you headed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have to go see someone in the inner walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren wants to join the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, what are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how many people die outside those walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You clearly don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see and understand the world outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die inside these walls without knowing what's out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If no one takes on their jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then those who lost their lives will have died in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My ship's here, I must get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, dear! Help me convince Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Carla, nothing can suppress a human's curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After I've returned, I'll show you the basement that I've been keeping you away from.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be joining something stupid like the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are content living like livestock are more stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, heretic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you punch me if you want to prove me wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stoop so low.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beating me up because you know I'm right and you can't prove me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean you've admitted that you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with your crappy arguments!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a moron. He's back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he want to get his ass handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll teach you a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-Mikasa's with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they ran away after seeing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they ran away after seeing Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stand up by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, after telling them that mankind needs to go outside eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They beat me, calling me a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want go outside. Why does everyone hate us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's been peaceful living inside these walls for the past 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Titans might be let inside when people leave the walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so the King's government banned people from showing interest to the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're risking our own lives. No one has the right to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa! How dare you tell my parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember agreeing to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they weren't happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,People are crazy for believing that these walls will protect us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the walls have been intact for the past 100 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that can guarantee they won't be broken down today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it an explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding... That wall is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,50 meters tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans are inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My house is over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans have invaded this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our house is definitely safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I turn this corner, our \Nhouse will be there like always!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to move this piece of wood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans are getting close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, take Mikasa and run. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to run too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs have been crushed by the debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run even if I get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry you and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just listen to what I say for once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just listen to me! Just one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, all three of us will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hannes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the kids and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take me lightly, Carla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill the Titan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And save all three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! You can't fight it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hannes-san! What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom is still trapped in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\b1}Stop!!!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, mankind received a grim reminder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We lived in fear of the Titans,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and were disgraced to live in these cages we called walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:06.69,Default,,200,200,0,,The small, closed-off areas surrounding the walls, such as Shiganshina, were used as baits to attract the Titans,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,fulfilling their roles of lowering costs of defense and military.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result of this design,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:20.98,Default,,300,300,0,,The people of Shiganshina could escape the assault of the Titans by traversing only one gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Toss all luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We might even fit one more if you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Eren and Mikasa aren't here yet.…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship is full! We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let us on! Even just my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't close it yet! Just wait a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've still got people out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If they break through this gate, we'll lose much more than just this small district!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind will be pushed back to the next wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean it's okay to just sacrifice all those people!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and close it! The Titans are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and close the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Run! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Close the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans will eat us all...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.90,0:24:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.15,0:24:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be able to go home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.27,0:24:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.55,0:24:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.81,0:24:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.52,0:24:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I... Us humans are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.38,0:24:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're weak, we can do nothing but cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.63,0:24:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll erase their existence from this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.70,0:24:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.67,0:24:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.29,0:24:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.46,0:25:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a single one of them will be left...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.31,0:25:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.04,0:25:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Holocaust" was the price of overconfidence and peace of 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.67,0:25:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, mankind was unaware of the existence of monsters such as the Colossus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.94,0:25:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wall Maria was lost and Wall Rose became humanity's last shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.84,0:25:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Always fearing that someday the Colossus would appear again and bring it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.64,0:25:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have graduated from the Military Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.05,0:25:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon you will become the wind of hope that will carry the dreams and hopes of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.48,0:26:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands upon your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.33,0:26:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.40,0:26:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For you trainees graduating today, three paths now open before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.79,0:26:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be stationed at the walls and defend the cities as members of the Garrison!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.04,0:26:16.20,Default,,300,300,0,,You can put your lives on the line to fight the Titans in their own territory as members of the Survey Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.71,0:26:21.24,Default,,225,225,0,,Or you can serve the King by controlling the crowds and protecting order as members of the Military Police Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.22,0:26:28.27,Default,,300,300,0,,Of course, only ten people with top scores we announced earlier are allowed into the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.95,0:26:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\i1\b0}Finally, I made it this far.{\i0\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.28,0:26:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\b0\i1}Now, it'll be our turn to devour the Titans!{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.99,0:26:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it! I'm in the Military Police now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never worry about having food again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.36,0:26:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean, do you know which division you will join?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.06,0:26:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? The Military Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.73,0:27:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I strived to be among the top ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.84,0:27:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I too want to join the Military Police
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.70,0:27:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no higher honor than working near the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.68,0:27:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.46,0:27:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being such a goody-goody and just tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.42,0:27:20.64,Default,,300,300,0,,You want to join the Military Police so you can live a simple, comfortable life within the Inner District.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.61,0:27:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys think the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.86,0:27:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.30,0:27:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We would prefer not having to go beyond the wall…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.63,0:27:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.18,0:27:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.48,0:27:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I will also enlist in the Military Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.05,0:27:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.73,0:27:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,, But...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.26,0:27:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump me together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.25,0:27:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So life on the interior is simple and comfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.72,0:27:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, this place was also part of the interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.80,0:27:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.66,0:28:02.46,Default,,300,300,0,,Jean, you're such a simpleton, you'd be comfortable living a life in blindness and ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.57,0:28:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.49,0:28:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even know how many people have been devoured?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.04,0:28:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Four years ago, when we had to leave the territory do to the forces of the Titans,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.99,0:28:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity became enraged and decided to launch a final offensive in desperation,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.34,0:28:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,, but were annihilated as mere fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.52,0:28:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the answer they found:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.59,0:28:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity can not cope with the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.32,0:28:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of that…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.01,0:28:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna give up without even trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.25,0:29:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We are mankind's last hope! \NThat's why we trained all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.50,0:29:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have made many sacrifices to obtain all this information on the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.40,0:29:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you say that we should just let ourselves be defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.30,0:29:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.31,0:29:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I... will enter the Survey Corps and end the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.58,0:29:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.07,0:29:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a deluded fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.12,0:29:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who enlists the Survey Corps by choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.89,0:29:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're so eager to die beyond the wall, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.66,0:29:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.49,0:29:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.52,0:29:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.45,0:29:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The instructor is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.82,0:29:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.40,0:29:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.70,0:29:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.12,0:29:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to put me down! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.38,0:30:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of other people's business!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.42,0:30:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get angry, you become too foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.57,0:30:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.01,0:30:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to join the Survey Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.19,0:30:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.92,0:30:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our top theoretician! Put that to better use!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.24,0:30:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I die as long as I can be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.94,0:30:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the Survey Corps too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.34,0:30:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the top score, didn't you? Go to the military police!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.39,0:30:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the military police if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.55,0:30:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to the Garrisons, so will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.36,0:30:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die an early death if I'm not there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.04,0:30:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.17,0:30:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose what's left of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.86,0:31:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You enlisted in the Survey Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.98,0:31:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Connie, you were going on and on about joining the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.83,0:31:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.69,0:31:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like he was listening to your lecture yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.82,0:31:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.25,0:31:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my own decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.23,0:31:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so shy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.68,0:31:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.17,0:31:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thomas... Are you serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.69,0:31:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.40,0:31:57.48,Default,,200,200,0,,I borrowed some meat from the officers' morning rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.26,0:32:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha... You wanna get solitary confinement?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.86,0:32:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.54,0:32:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Real idiocy's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.30,0:32:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all split it up together later.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.95,0:32:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll slice it up and eat it with bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.16,0:32:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.22,0:32:16.59,Default,,200,200,0,,Yeah! Meat is a luxury now that we've lost so much land!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.11,0:32:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.59,0:32:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we retake the land, we can keep pigs and cows again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.76,0:32:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.80,0:32:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, so save my part!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.21,0:32:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.60,0:32:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.39,0:32:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.59,0:32:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll find us out if we don't get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.40,0:32:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a while before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.92,0:32:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years have passed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.95,0:33:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind's finally regaining its dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.33,0:33:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.97,0:33:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind's counterattack begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.63,0:33:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.06,0:33:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Samuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.36,0:33:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.81,0:33:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Samuel! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.48,0:33:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.02,0:34:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate's... broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.08,0:34:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Again... The Titans will get in again!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.47,0:34:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Every... fucking... one...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.92,0:34:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready the artillery! Four groups! Prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.87,0:34:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The target's right in front of us! It's the Colossal Titan!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.92,0:34:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance! Don't let it slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.56,0:34:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there. It's been 5 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.28,0:35:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\i1\b0}It aimed for the cannons!{\i0\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.80,0:35:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\b0\i1}So it wasn't just a coincidence that he targeted the gate!{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.70,0:35:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\i1\b0}He's actually...{\i0\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.80,0:35:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\b0\i1}Intelligent!{\b1\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.14,0:35:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\i1\b0}Still, this is our chance.{\i0\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.06,0:35:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\i1\b0}This is the only one that can destroy the gates.{\i0\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.51,0:35:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\i1\b0}If I can just stop him!{\i0\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.75,0:35:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.85,0:35:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.63,0:35:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.81,0:35:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.82,0:36:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\i1}Did I miss?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.81,0:36:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No... The Colossal Titan vanished...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.07,0:36:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.03,0:36:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's the same as five years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.99,0:36:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared, just as suddenly as he appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.93,0:36:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring only your most critical possessions!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.18,0:36:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remain calm and evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.59,0:36:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If they break through, the hell of five years ago will be repeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.40,0:36:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We must stop the Titans here!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.84,0:36:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You recruits have completed training and graduated into proper soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.70,0:37:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you to actively participate in this operation too!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.34,0:37:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Hannah. I swear I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.72,0:37:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.58,0:37:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Armin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.03,0:37:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.18,0:37:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pull it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.93,0:37:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're still in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.59,0:37:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got an eight-meter hole in the wall, and no way to fix it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.57,0:37:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't even dig out that giant rock near Zemo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.69,0:37:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's only a matter of time until they break through Wall Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.29,0:37:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.05,0:37:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! This time it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.24,0:37:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind won't lose to the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.27,0:37:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry. I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.11,0:38:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be today?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.35,0:38:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to go to the interior tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.34,0:38:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.42,0:38:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.56,0:38:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.41,0:38:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jean! What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.41,0:38:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that crap, you suicidal asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.08,0:38:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.97,0:38:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just chill out and accept my death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.95,0:38:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.80,0:38:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember our three years of training!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.18,0:38:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been on the verge of death many times during those three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.87,0:38:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Some actually died.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.00,0:38:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Some ran away, and some were sent away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.31,0:38:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But we survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.43,0:38:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.87,0:38:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna survive today too!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.26,0:39:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll survive today, and you're bloody well going to interior tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.65,0:39:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.77,0:39:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Daz!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.38,0:39:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't cower there forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.34,0:39:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! If the battle gets too chaotic, come find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.46,0:39:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? We're in totally different squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.86,0:39:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of the fray, nothing goes according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.34,0:39:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.91,0:39:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going on about…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.99,0:39:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Trainee Ackerman!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.40,0:39:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,, You were specially assigned to rear guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.47,0:39:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.37,0:39:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd only be in the way there, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.38,0:39:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The evacuation is going slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.16,0:39:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We need as many elite guards as possible protecting the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.28,0:39:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.02,0:39:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.25,0:39:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so unlike you to panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.76,0:39:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind is on the brink of extinction!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.06,0:39:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No one gives a fuck about what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.16,0:40:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I lost my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.01,0:40:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one thing. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.78,0:40:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.26,0:40:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.71,0:40:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't die even if I were killed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.62,0:40:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know anything about this world yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.94,0:40:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.21,0:40:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think this is a great chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.97,0:40:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If we prove ourselves here in this first battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.66,0:40:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,before even entering the Survey Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.86,0:40:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,surely they'll promote us right up the ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.75,0:41:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.33,0:41:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to burst your bubble,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.70,0:41:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But quite a few of us are aiming for the Survey Corps this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.18,0:41:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I lagged behind you earlier, Eren,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.16,0:41:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not losing this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.61,0:41:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Thomas!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.63,0:41:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a contest to see who can slay more Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.85,0:41:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No fudging your numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.13,0:41:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad 34, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.01,0:41:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Assist the frontline guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.06,0:41:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.65,0:41:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.87,0:41:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans advanced this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.90,0:41:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The front guard's already been crushed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.29,0:41:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are our glory-hound seniors doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.51,0:41:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I expected the situation to be bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.36,0:42:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\i1}but this...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.89,0:42:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,An abnormal one!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.03,0:42:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.34,0:42:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you, motherfucker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.68,0:42:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.47,0:42:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.75,0:42:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.62,0:42:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you eat Thomas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.92,0:43:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.26,0:43:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.77,0:43:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.36,0:43:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.96,0:43:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why... am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.25,0:43:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watching... as my comrades... get eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.31,0:43:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why... won't my body... move?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.35,0:44:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Eren! Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.48,0:44:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it now, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.98,0:44:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this book my grandpa was hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.87,0:44:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about the outside world!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.42,0:44:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The outside world?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.97,0:44:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's forbidden, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.94,0:44:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the Military Police find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.40,0:44:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.28,0:44:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,According to this book,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.54,0:44:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the world is covered by a huge amount of water called "sea"!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.62,0:44:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all salty water too!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.40,0:44:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.26,0:44:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more than just mountains of salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.94,0:44:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire water! A continent of ice! Snowfields of sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.48,0:44:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The world out there must be far more vast than the inside of the walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.98,0:44:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The outside world...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.34,0:44:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.08,0:44:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if we could explore the outside world too someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.94,0:45:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.53,0:45:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm gonna die here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.68,0:45:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Armin... You told me about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.91,0:45:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going... to the outside world...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.04,0:45:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.07,0:46:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.58,0:46:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.46,0:46:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ahold of yourself! Hey! Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.79,0:46:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Armin! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.54,0:46:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with me now? Are you okay? Hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.93,0:46:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.26,0:46:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My... squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.05,0:46:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, get it together already! Why are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.70,0:46:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you so... slimy?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.71,0:46:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.16,0:46:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm useless! Just leave me to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.88,0:46:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.53,0:46:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.96,0:46:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just drop it already, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.16,0:47:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all dead... Everyone but him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.17,0:47:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Armin didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.00,0:47:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes and look the fuck around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.09,0:47:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to babysit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.29,0:47:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he unhurt then?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.51,0:47:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Maybe the Titans mistook him for dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.11,0:47:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just bad luck their squad \Nencountered multiple Titans at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.46,0:47:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think this guy was the sole survivor? \NEren and the others didn't deserve this ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.34,0:47:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you heartless bitch, you want me to shut your mouth for good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.75,0:47:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you two! Of course everyone's on edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.92,0:47:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our friends are dying all around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.77,0:47:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.30,0:47:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Krista! After this mission ends, marry me, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.04,0:47:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true... She's screwing around even more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.34,0:47:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, we can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.21,0:47:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.01,0:47:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.81,0:48:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go join the rear guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.04,0:48:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.92,0:48:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta go, Connie!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.10,0:48:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been ordered to move ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.29,0:48:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.31,0:48:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, this world hasn't become hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.61,0:48:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just didn't get it up until right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.16,0:48:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This world's been hell all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.26,0:48:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The strong feed upon the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.54,0:48:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's such an obligingly simple rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.80,0:48:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Except in this world, my friends tried to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.37,0:48:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They helped me, though I was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.95,0:49:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To the two of them, I was always someone to be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.55,0:49:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to become strong like them,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.05,0:49:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we could walk together side-by-side as we lived out our lives in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.43,0:49:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just look where that got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.21,0:49:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my fault that Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.94,0:49:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hannah, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.51,0:49:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.92,0:49:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz isn't breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.58,0:49:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been performing CPR over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.85,0:49:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.87,0:49:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hannah, it's dangerous here! We should hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.03,0:49:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And just leave Franz behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.40,0:50:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it, Hannah...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.80,0:50:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.54,0:50:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop... No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.58,0:50:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... take this anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.50,0:50:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even understand the situation we're in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.64,0:50:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.10,0:50:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jean! What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.08,0:50:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally received the order to retreat,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.56,0:50:46.60,Default,,200,200,0,,But we can't get over the wall because we're out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.45,0:50:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.54,0:50:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to those fucking cowards...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.05,0:50:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the support squads?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.15,0:50:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.85,0:50:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they all dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.33,0:51:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably lost their will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.21,0:51:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.37,0:51:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt they've abandoned their mission and barricaded themselves away in the HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.11,0:51:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing the Titans have them surrounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.51,0:51:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why they can't supply us with gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.36,0:51:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I had such a boring life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.13,0:51:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone told me beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.15,0:51:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Reiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.43,0:51:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not time yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.46,0:51:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We must group up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.86,0:51:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.22,0:51:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what we do, we'll be \Ndead before we make it out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.91,0:51:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm prepared to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.21,0:51:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But what exactly am I going to die for?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.66,0:51:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa! Weren't you with the rear guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.91,0:51:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie! I think I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.03,0:51:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I apologize for bothering you,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.24,0:51:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but have you seen Eren's unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.45,0:51:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, and I haven't seen anyone climb the wall either.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.68,0:52:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin's over there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.19,0:52:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.57,0:52:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mikasa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.18,0:52:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap! How can I look her in the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.43,0:52:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.06,0:52:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.99,0:52:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.69,0:52:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Our unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.72,0:52:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The 34th cadet unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.06,0:52:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thomas Wagner.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.81,0:52:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nic Tius.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.89,0:52:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mylius Zeramuski.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.54,0:52:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.91,0:52:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.47,0:52:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All five of them have fulfilled their duty
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.00,0:53:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and died heroic deaths in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.59,0:53:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.67,0:53:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So the 34th unit was nearly wiped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.17,0:53:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fight the Titans, we'll end up like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.67,0:53:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.02,0:53:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren died in place of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.71,0:53:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.18,0:53:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.76,0:53:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.40,0:53:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.13,0:53:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.88,0:53:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.98,0:53:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco, If we take out the Titans around the HQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.99,0:53:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we can replenish our gas supplies and climb the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.45,0:53:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.00,0:54:02.19,Default,,200,200,0,,Yeah... But even if you're with us, there's just too many...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.30,0:54:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.00,0:54:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.55,0:54:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than all of you. Extremely strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.93,0:54:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can kill all those Titans there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.58,0:54:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.89,0:54:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're either incompetent or you're spineless cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.86,0:54:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.79,0:54:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sit here and suck on your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.34,0:54:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.29,0:54:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.45,0:54:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.10,0:54:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to fight all those Titans by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.07,0:54:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.82,0:54:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't, then I'll just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.62,0:54:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I win, I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.05,0:54:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless I fight, I cannot win.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.62,0:54:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.06,0:54:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your oratory skills are what's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.34,0:54:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the point of that to shock us into action?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.63,0:54:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.88,0:55:04.81,Default,,200,200,0,,Hey! Were we trained to let our comrades fight alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.23,0:55:07.70,Default,,200,200,0,,At this rate, we're going to turn out to be spineless cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.96,0:55:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised I'd hear him say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.54,0:55:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Cowards! Weaklings! Retards!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.27,0:55:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're nuts... {\i0}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.26,0:55:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.85,0:55:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Follow Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.79,0:55:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep this fight short!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.32,0:55:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to kill them all before we run out of gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.16,0:55:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa's just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.69,0:55:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How can she move that fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.16,0:55:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's using too much gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.23,0:55:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll run out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.40,0:55:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't care how skilled she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.86,0:55:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without our agility, we can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.23,0:56:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she keeps this up...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.59,0:56:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.27,0:56:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.37,0:56:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean! You lead the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.20,0:56:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.80,0:56:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.52,0:56:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?! There are more Titans left!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.44,0:56:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We need your skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.06,0:56:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.57,0:56:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.05,0:56:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lost my family once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.89,0:56:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This pain is familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.47,0:56:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will I have to start fresh once again?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.87,0:57:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This world is cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.62,0:57:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's also... Very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.17,0:57:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.34,0:57:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go... Back to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.94,0:57:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lived a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.65,0:58:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.76,0:58:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I'd given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.98,0:58:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.51,0:58:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I struggling?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.71,0:58:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.90,0:58:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My life has no meaning anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.06,0:58:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's keeping me going?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.45,0:58:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.75,0:58:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.88,0:58:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! You must fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.63,0:59:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.30,0:59:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.72,0:59:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never give up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.42,0:59:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I died,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.94,0:59:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be4\blur2\i1}I wouldn't be able to remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.91,0:59:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'll win, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.48,0:59:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll survive, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.42,0:59:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.14,1:00:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A Titan... is killing... another Titan...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.80,1:00:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please be all right, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.09,1:00:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.94,1:00:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.60,1:00:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.75,1:00:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.91,1:00:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We must get going!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.65,1:00:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! There are two 15 meter classes!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.63,1:00:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That Titan's...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.15,1:01:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It finished the other Titan off? \NIt knew of a Titan's weak point?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.97,1:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We must get going before it comes this way!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.04,1:01:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It doesn't care about us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.06,1:01:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It could've attacked us long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.06,1:01:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like it had an idea of how to perform hand-to-hand combat.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.29,1:01:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.98,1:01:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just consider it an abnormal!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.92,1:01:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we must hurry to the HQ!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.10,1:01:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.02,1:01:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An idea?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.17,1:02:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't we take advantage of this Titan?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.80,1:02:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Open way!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.25,1:02:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.77,1:02:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many of us made it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.53,1:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many died on my command?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.37,1:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're part of the supply squad, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.88,1:03:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Jean!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.02,1:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,These bastards abandoned us!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.24,1:03:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even have a clue how many died?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.26,1:03:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans invaded the supply depot! What could we have done?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.55,1:03:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your job to figure something out!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.98,1:03:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take cover!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.95,1:03:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! There are too many people gathered here!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.61,1:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Inside!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.03,1:03:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.02,1:03:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Mikasa?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.65,1:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She crashed back there! She's been eaten!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.47,1:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is normal... This is reality, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.55,1:04:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was I just chasing a delusional dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.37,1:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just thinking about it, it's obvious...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.93,1:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way to beat these gigantic monstrosities.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.76,1:04:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.40,1:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.56,1:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa?!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.65,1:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's empty... We did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.81,1:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We just barely made it!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.32,1:04:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... all alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.45,1:04:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Armin!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.46,1:04:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.11,1:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plan was a success!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.88,1:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! That Titan's an abnormality that slaughters other Titans!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.09,1:05:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even interested in attacking humans!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.51,1:05:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If we play our cards right,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.47,1:05:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all get outta here alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.34,1:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd... use the Titan?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.62,1:05:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd rely on a Titan's help? \NThat's more delusional than any dream!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.78,1:05:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.81,1:05:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if it's an abnormal or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.36,1:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it rampage here for as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.67,1:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Realistically, that's our best option for survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.31,1:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We found some!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.66,1:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Military Police supplies,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.27,1:05:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they are covered in dust...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.31,1:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Will three bullets be enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.57,1:06:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do these guns even work against the Titans in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.05,1:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.96,1:06:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if there are still seven 3-4 meter class Titans in the supply room,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.16,1:06:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Blinding them all at once isn't impossible with this much firepower.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.41,1:06:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,First we'll use the lift to lower a large number of people into the center of the chamber.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.09,1:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, they'll fire directly into the faces of all seven Titans at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.67,1:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll blind them.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.44,1:06:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The next instance will decide everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.46,1:06:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven other people hiding near the ceiling will swoop down to attack their weak spots while they're blind.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.72,1:06:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words... if we follow this plan, we'll be gambling everything on this single attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.67,1:06:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole point is for seven people to kill all seven Titans simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.79,1:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The seven people should be the most physically capable ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.63,1:07:01.74,Default,,200,200,0,,You'll have to shoulder the burden of everyone's lives...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.74,1:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.39,1:07:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.87,1:07:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever fails, all of us will die.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.00,1:07:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The risk is the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.32,1:07:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I'm a nobody.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.74,1:07:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my plan really the best option?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.00,1:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no other choices except your plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.83,1:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time left to think. This idea's our only shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.95,1:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we've just gotta give it everything we've got.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.15,1:07:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Be confident.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.86,1:07:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a talent for reasoning out the best solution.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.42,1:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The lift's ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.33,1:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The guns too!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.63,1:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them are loaded!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.42,1:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You just aren't aware yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.12,1:07:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you more later.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.26,1:07:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.88,1:08:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all good. There's still only seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.37,1:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the plan!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.92,1:08:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Lure them in closer!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.61,1:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.55,1:08:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We shouldn't fight at a disadvantage
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.42,1:08:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if we want to keep casualties to the bare minimum.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.20,1:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must end it in this one strike!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.00,1:08:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.42,1:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.25,1:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.57,1:09:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got it! The others?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.93,1:09:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me... for suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.75,1:09:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,stabbing you... from behind...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.30,1:09:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sasha and Connie!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.74,1:09:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Help them!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.54,1:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.21,1:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa! You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.84,1:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.93,1:09:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm safe, thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.14,1:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then stand! Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.69,1:09:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.30,1:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.37,1:10:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez. That was too close, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.43,1:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you weren't injured.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.27,1:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We got them all!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.24,1:10:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone stock up on supplies!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.94,1:10:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.34,1:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all ready? Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.01,1:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta bail now!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.55,1:10:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Go! We need to meet up with the main units!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.89,1:10:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.40,1:10:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.75,1:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.67,1:10:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That Titan...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.92,1:10:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're eating it...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.75,1:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Its body can't regenerate?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.54,1:10:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought uncovering the truth about that Titan might be the key
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.40,1:10:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to freeing ourselves from this desperate situation...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.84,1:10:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.54,1:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If they just rip it to shreds like that, then we won't have learned a single thing!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.45,1:11:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get rid of those Titans currently devouring it,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.57,1:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And at least try to keep it alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.17,1:11:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you insane, Reiner?!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.68,1:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We can finally escape this deathtrap!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.64,1:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if that Titan could become an ally?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.90,1:11:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it'd be a weapon more powerful than any cannon?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.91,1:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our... ally? Are you for real?!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.82,1:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.83,1:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The abnormal that ate Thomas!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.19,1:11:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.49,1:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about helping it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.35,1:12:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it burnt itself out.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.30,1:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.96,1:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that monster's on our side!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.76,1:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Titans are Titans.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.17,1:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.30,1:12:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.89,1:14:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Eren...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.19,1:14:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's even got his limbs back...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.01,1:14:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eren was eaten by that Titan back then.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.89,1:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened here?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.93,1:14:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Eren... did all of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.25,1:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the reasons why the Titans' attack on Trost claimed so many soldiers' lives
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.18,1:15:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the elite Survey Corps were absent.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.96,1:15:10.76,Default,,200,200,0,,They'd left on a mission outside the Wall that very morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.25,1:15:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here! It's the main force of the Survey Corps!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.27,1:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Erwin! Kick their Titan asses for me!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.49,1:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There's Captain Levi!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.52,1:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They say in battle, he's as strong as a whole brigade!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.00,1:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.70,1:15:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they wouldn't worship you so much if they knew what an obsessive clean freak you are!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.24,1:15:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,An expedition with the aim of exploring the outside and look for possible settlement.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.37,1:15:46.62,Default,,200,200,0,,When troops advanced into Titan \Nterritory, casualties exceeded 30%.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.07,1:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how great the power gap between Titans and men was.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.70,1:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... Just watch... You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.43,1:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind will... survive...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.40,1:16:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards... will all... Fall to Captain Levi!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.52,1:16:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One on the right...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.83,1:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Two on the left.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.67,1:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, I've gathered the reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.34,1:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra, look after that soldier down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.43,1:16:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you attack the one to the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.87,1:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clean up on the left.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.07,1:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely bunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.84,1:16:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You all have such interesting faces.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.65,1:16:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.77,1:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'll never get...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.69,1:17:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A clean cut of your flesh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.75,1:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It got all filthy...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.10,1:17:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, I can't stop the bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.31,1:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.04,1:17:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.82,1:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I... useful to... mankind?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.86,1:17:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will I die... useless like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.34,1:18:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.23,1:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll do even more.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.89,1:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your spirit will stay with me and give me strength!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.66,1:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.26,1:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I will exterminate the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.32,1:18:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, he's gone...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.39,1:18:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he hear everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.99,1:18:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he heard it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.54,1:18:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's resting so peacefully now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.39,1:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, then...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.54,1:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Levi! We're going back!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.16,1:18:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Back? We haven't reached our limit yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.25,1:18:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did my men die in vain?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.34,1:19:03.33,Default,,200,200,0,,The Titans have all started heading north towards the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.84,1:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.08,1:19:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's happened in the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.21,1:19:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They might've even broken through the Wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.88,1:19:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All cadets are to ready their equipment and stand by!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.01,1:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how we managed to refill our gas and get out of Trost.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.89,1:19:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, then the people who aren't here are all...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.35,1:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.27,1:19:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Mikasa?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.45,1:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I thought Mikasa came back late with Jean and the others...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.73,1:19:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean! Don't tell me Mikasa was wounded?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.02,1:19:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.92,1:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We were sworn to keep it secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.66,1:20:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.68,1:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.50,1:20:12.60,Default,,200,200,0,,It's hardly something they can keep covered up though.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.44,1:20:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon all of mankind will know about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.86,1:20:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Although for that, they must pass this test and gain their survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.88,1:20:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.28,1:20:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Armin! We're going up!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.66,1:20:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannon fire?!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.88,1:20:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But why just on shot?!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.58,1:20:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...\NIs that smoke from a Titan?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.70,1:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.72,1:21:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.06,1:21:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we get them?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.14,1:21:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.32,1:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that! Stay back! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.44,1:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand by on alert!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.74,1:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand by!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.94,1:21:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Load the next round into the cannon!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.72,1:22:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.44,1:22:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.60,1:22:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.20,1:22:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know is I've got my arm and leg back as if by magic,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.34,1:22:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that all the Garrison sees is a Titan who killed his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.84,1:22:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, when I transformed,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.96,1:22:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.24,1:22:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if I wasn't able to control my body!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.62,1:22:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I did remember one thing, though...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.76,1:22:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The basement. The basement of my old house.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.22,1:22:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My father said I would understand everything if I went there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.84,1:22:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Always keep this key with you. Never let go of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.64,1:22:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you look at it, remember!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.94,1:22:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You must go to the basement!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.40,1:23:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood? Retake Wall Maria and reach that basement!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.10,1:23:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This power will prove usefull then!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.68,1:23:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's the reason all of this is happening to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.24,1:23:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get to that basement, I'll probably find out the truth about Titans.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.72,1:23:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Why did he hide this from me?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.00,1:23:29.74,Default,,200,200,0,,It's the intel the Survey Corps has been searching for, \Nat the cost of thousands of lives!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.26,1:23:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mankind's last hope!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.42,1:23:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just keeping it locked away in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.18,1:23:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.32,1:23:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, your nose is bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.06,1:23:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really pale. Your breathing's heavy too.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.98,1:23:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing that clearly puts too much strain on your body!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.68,1:23:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I'm in bad shape right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.84,1:23:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've caused you enough trouble already.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.14,1:24:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on out, I'm doing this alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.78,1:24:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.50,1:24:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.58,1:24:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.56,1:24:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.04,1:24:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't keep up with you, then don't concern yourself with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.40,1:24:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have to do whatever you say either.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.42,1:24:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap already, for fuck's sake!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.34,1:24:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not your little brother or your kid!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.68,1:24:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess that even in my final moments, I'm still nothing more than a coward.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.66,1:24:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've helped me out so many times,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.20,1:24:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet never once was I able to repay them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.72,1:24:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After this... The three of us will never be together again.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.86,1:25:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! I can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.12,1:25:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There has to be a way out!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.94,1:25:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll convince them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.82,1:25:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to show them you don't intend to resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.46,1:25:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's been troubling me ever since I saw Eren fight as a Titan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.55,1:25:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't even sorted out my own \Nthoughts yet, but I've got to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.50,1:25:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to think while I speak!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.48,1:25:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.52,1:25:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally showed your true colors, monster!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.30,1:25:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll signal! I'll signal the cannon!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.68,1:25:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't the enemy of mankind!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.23,1:25:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're willing to share all the intelligence we've gathered!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.45,1:25:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Begging for your lives is useless now!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.23,1:26:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen it with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.30,1:26:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A Titan came from inside of another!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.46,1:26:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that weren't enough, I also witnessed how Eren Jeager got out from that Titan's neck!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.38,1:26:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say he's not an enemy, prove it!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.12,1:26:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for further proof!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.38,1:26:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right! It's unnecessary!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.38,1:26:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The issue isn't how we see him!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.88,1:26:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.12,1:26:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You said everybody saw him!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.92,1:26:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they must've seen him fighting the Titans too!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.30,1:26:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And they must've seen all the Titans ganging up against him!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.62,1:26:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans see him as prey, just like the rest of mankind!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.66,1:26:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing you say can change that fact!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.76,1:26:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A Titan as an ally... That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.64,1:26:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.52,1:27:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall for this clever trap!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.20,1:27:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As a soldier, I swore to devote my heart to the resurrection of mankind!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.08,1:27:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no greater glory than dying for that belief!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.66,1:27:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If we added his Titan power to the might of our armies,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.32,1:27:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It might even be possible to recapture the town!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.82,1:27:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For the glory of the human race, I beg you! In my final moments before I die,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.86,1:27:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Permit me to explain his strategic importance!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.24,1:27:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we should consider wh—
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.77,1:27:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.84,1:27:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how they plead for their lives, they're still rebels!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.56,1:27:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who break the rules must be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.84,1:27:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.00,1:27:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out already.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.76,1:28:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed. As big as you are, \Nyou've still got the guts of a scared fawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.48,1:28:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Pixis?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.74,1:28:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see how magnificent his salute is?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.90,1:28:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just arrived, but the situation has already been relayed to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.52,1:28:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You go organize the reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.16,1:28:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be worthwhile to hear what they've got to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.86,1:28:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot Pixis.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.02,1:28:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Commander-in-Chief of the defense of the southern territories, including Trost.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.88,1:28:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A man entrusted with complete authority over the key area of mankind's defenses.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.18,1:28:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you believe that basement holds all the answers you seek?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.32,1:28:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Will you believe me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.52,1:28:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Since even you yourself can't say for sure, let's just say I'll just keep it in mind for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.96,1:29:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadet Arlert, was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.98,1:29:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.16,1:29:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you said that by using this "Titan power"
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.84,1:29:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to retake this city.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.26,1:29:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really believe that,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.30,1:29:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Or were you just desperate to stay alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.37,1:29:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... both, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.90,1:29:23.95,Default,,200,200,0,,I was trying to say that Eren could take on his Titan form,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.86,1:29:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry that boulder to the wall, and block the gap in the gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.98,1:29:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought just occurred to me...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.80,1:29:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But couldn't you look at Eren's power as a chance to turn this situation to our favor?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.46,1:29:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I was also desperate to save our lives...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.22,1:29:54.66,Default,,100,100,0,,Desperate to save... Those words are worth more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.18,1:30:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Cadet Jaeger?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.52,1:30:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.02,1:30:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you close the gap?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.54,1:30:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.96,1:30:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.63,1:30:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand this any more than the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.30,1:30:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be irresponsible of me to answer as if I knew either way.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.98,1:30:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.82,1:30:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the wrong question.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.65,1:30:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do it or not? Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.63,1:31:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it. I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.87,1:31:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not certain I can close the gap, but I'll still do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.18,1:31:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The elite team has commenced the operation.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.41,1:31:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now brief you about the operation for retaking Trost!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.51,1:31:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall now introduce him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.40,1:31:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger of the Cadets!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.89,1:31:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He can summon a Titan body and control it at will!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.39,1:31:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He will transform into a Titan, pick up that giant boulder near the front gate,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.32,1:32:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,carry it to the breach in the wall, and block off the hole with it!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.58,1:32:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission will be to protect him from the other Titans
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.85,1:32:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...while he's carrying the boulder to the breach!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.98,1:32:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger's protection will be entrusted to the squad leaders:
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.01,1:32:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian Dietrich, Rico Brzenska and Mitabi Jarnach!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.98,1:32:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of mankind is in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.70,1:32:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.26,1:32:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.68,1:32:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the Titans first appeared,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.16,1:32:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not once has mankind won against them!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.52,1:32:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans keep marching forth and we keep retreating,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.06,1:32:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting them take our land!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.00,1:32:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when this plan succeeds,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.06,1:33:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the first time we've ever reconquered land from the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.94,1:33:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that moment, for the first time, mankind will triumph over the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.87,1:33:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to what's been taken from us,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.64,1:33:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a small thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.63,1:33:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will mean mankind has finally managed an attack on the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.25,1:34:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By human standards, that rock is way too heavy to lift.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.23,1:34:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm sure Eren has the strength to guide us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.66,1:34:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eren?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.86,1:34:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ackerman!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.13,1:34:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, don't you recognize me? I'm Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.48,1:34:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your family!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.00,1:34:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You must block the hole with that boulder!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.50,1:35:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodge, Ackerman!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.76,1:35:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.66,1:35:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a stupid Titan like all the rest!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.78,1:35:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.51,1:35:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad leader Ian!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.29,1:35:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Two approaching from ahead!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.07,1:35:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One 10-meter and one 6-meter class!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.60,1:35:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Another is coming from behind!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.18,1:35:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,, It's a 12-meter class!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.53,1:35:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation has failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.90,1:35:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was obvious from the start that no secret weapon existed.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.48,1:35:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.26,1:35:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.65,1:35:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they... fail?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.55,1:35:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.10,1:35:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.57,1:36:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Pixis,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.27,1:36:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We should fall back to defending the gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.32,1:36:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you approve?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.37,1:36:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.17,1:36:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Order the elite team to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.27,1:36:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.17,1:36:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep luring the Titans to the corner of the town.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.04,1:36:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the elite team, they have the authority to act as they see fit.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.33,1:36:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't merely just skilled soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.59,1:36:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the elite among the elite that I entrusted with the future of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.13,1:36:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving up so easily would be unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.33,1:36:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot allow our comrades' deaths to be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.44,1:36:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We must struggle to our very last breaths.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.42,1:37:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm at home?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.05,1:37:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I need sleep...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.32,1:37:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good! Behind us!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.35,1:37:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A 13-meter class is heading for Jaeger!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.64,1:37:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,More Titans are coming in through the gate!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.18,1:37:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like four 10-meter class!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.73,1:37:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ackerman, handle the one behind us!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.43,1:37:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.27,1:37:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them reach Jaeger!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.02,1:37:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop them here!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.24,1:37:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.59,1:37:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though they're the elite,\N just two squads can't handle four at once...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.59,1:38:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no... Why are there so many Titans?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.70,1:38:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are hardly any humans around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.21,1:38:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me... They're drawn to Eren?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.83,1:38:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.53,1:38:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.91,1:38:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.08,1:38:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Eren?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.00,1:38:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! Get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.96,1:38:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren can't control that Titan!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.20,1:38:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't respond even when I tried talking to it!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.76,1:38:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use in anyone else trying either!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.87,1:38:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.92,1:38:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.34,1:38:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave Eren behind,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.04,1:38:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone's fighting!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.52,1:38:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But with this many Titans,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.49,1:38:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're bound to get wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.42,1:38:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren came out of the Titan's weak point before.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.40,1:38:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.08,1:39:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be related to the mystery of the Titan's true nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.68,1:39:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. As long as I avoid the middle,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.26,1:39:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be fatal...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.06,1:39:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just going to hurt a bit!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.79,1:39:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.82,1:39:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.72,1:39:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa! Right now, do what you can!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.90,1:39:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go, there are lives you can save!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.54,1:39:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Eren to me and get going!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.31,1:39:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.69,1:39:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.41,1:39:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come out of there, we're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.73,1:39:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.29,1:39:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.59,1:39:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.96,1:40:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to avenging your mother?!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.83,1:40:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to exterminate all the Titans?!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.39,1:40:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you hate those bastards for killing your mom?!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.84,1:40:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.62,1:40:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom's right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.20,1:40:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.27,1:40:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Wake up, please! Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.14,1:40:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.65,1:40:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay here, we'll be killed by the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.03,1:40:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will end right here!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.87,1:40:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, you're making no sense, Armin.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.80,1:40:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I go outside?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.85,1:40:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Why should I...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.68,1:40:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Join the Recon Corps...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.23,1:40:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.06,1:41:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that, you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.26,1:41:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your distance!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.57,1:41:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ackerman reporting in!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.47,1:41:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join Mitabi's squad!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.43,1:41:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.29,1:41:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.20,1:41:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.50,1:41:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've had enough of people dying on my account!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.58,1:42:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, it just had to break right now?!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.71,1:42:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.07,1:42:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Why isn't he using his 3D Maneuver Gear?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.46,1:42:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it broke!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.77,1:42:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sort this out myself!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.10,1:43:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Eren! Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.78,1:43:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.38,1:43:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we going to explore the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.62,1:43:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Far, far beyond these walls...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.57,1:43:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To the burning water and the land of ice. \NTo the snowfields of sand.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.89,1:43:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd forgotten about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.97,1:43:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'd just stopped bringing it up because you didn't want me to join the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.82,1:43:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The outside world...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.01,1:43:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, answer me! Even though you knew hell was raging outside the walls...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.88,1:43:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ever want to see the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.54,1:44:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask? Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.19,1:44:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was born into this world!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.30,1:44:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad leader, this is all we can handle! We're the only ones left!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.47,1:44:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fall back to the rock!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.88,1:44:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.92,1:44:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Titans incoming from the gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.32,1:44:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.11,1:44:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.74,1:45:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be his Maneuver Gear!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.29,1:45:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.48,1:45:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you bastard! I'm in a hurry here!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.08,1:45:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.41,1:45:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.78,1:45:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, what a drag!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.42,1:45:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Why is the trigger so hard to pull?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.43,1:45:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.65,1:46:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.22,1:46:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line! Fly away already!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.44,1:46:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are insane!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.80,1:46:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My line again! I think I just died like three times over!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.37,1:46:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.51,1:47:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.96,1:47:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.16,1:47:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.69,1:47:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren won! He's trying to do his job now!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.94,1:47:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can just make it to the gate,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.40,1:47:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We win!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.16,1:47:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.42,1:47:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We must defend Eren until he reaches the gate, even if it costs us our lives!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.55,1:47:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let any Titans get near him!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.29,1:47:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep them all out of the way! We must support Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.32,1:48:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, go to Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.59,1:48:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order! Got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.41,1:48:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.58,1:48:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitabi's squad? What are they...?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.64,1:48:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans aren't paying us any attention! We've gotta get close enough that they can't ignore us!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.55,1:48:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.44,1:48:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around, or I'll shove my sword right up your stinkin' ass and bleed you to death!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.76,1:48:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Two of them are after us!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.96,1:48:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run to the buildings!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.12,1:48:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Staying on the ground is suicide!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.64,1:48:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Without horses or buildings, we can't fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.43,1:48:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's the only way we've got left.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.36,1:48:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone follow their lead!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.66,1:48:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, we're going too.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.71,1:49:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This way! Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.40,1:49:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My body... It feels like I'm being crushed...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.52,1:49:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa? Armin? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.30,1:49:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay down there, the Titans will eat you!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.23,1:49:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.37,1:49:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.58,1:49:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.51,1:49:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitabi!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.79,1:49:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did you ever want to see the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.18,1:49:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're born, all of us are free.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.18,1:50:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,People who deny that, no matter how strong they are, don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.18,1:50:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The burning water, the land of ice... I don't care what!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.83,1:50:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who saw such things would be the freest person in the entire world!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.09,1:50:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! Who would value their life over something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.06,1:50:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However terrifying the world may be... It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.63,1:50:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However cruel the world may be... It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.05,1:50:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.90,1:50:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.00,1:50:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.89,1:50:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.33,1:50:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out! Titans!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.93,1:50:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle this!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.00,1:51:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.96,1:51:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.12,1:51:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.49,1:52:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody... didn't die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.28,1:52:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, for the first time, mankind triumphed over the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.66,1:53:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of his body is still fused with the Titan.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.39,1:53:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't pull him out!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.90,1:53:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to cut it then!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.05,1:53:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you kids...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.00,1:53:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the situation here?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.57,1:53:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wings of... Freedom...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.04,1:58:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.29,1:58:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.17,1:58:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... am I?



